_:N7f060b83c3f0434dbcf78de121edd313 <http://schema.org/description> "The Women and Equalities Unit is part of the Office for Equality and Opportunity. We lead work on policy relating to gender equality, LGBT+ people and the overall framework of equality legislation in the UK. WEU is part of the Cabinet Office and the Office for Equality and Opportunity ." .
